      "title": "Migration task",
      "prompt": "For the migration, let's create a chain of task:\n\n- Add a check to force usage of this new API (allow list existing usages)\n- A task to validate the concept on a sub-set of items (surfacing potential issues)\n- A task to migrate users (using sub-agents to batch the refactoring)\n- A task to cleanup the allow-list, and cleanup legacy path. Validate only the new path can be used\n"
